strings:
<se_high>Red: I ain't your mate, got it!?
So get outta 'ere!
<se_low>Yangus: Wait a minute! I come all this way specially cos I got somefin' to ask ya!

<se_high>Red: Spit it out, then!
Wot is it!? Out wiv it!
<se_low>Yangus: Take it easy! I was just wonderin' if you've 'eard o' the Moonshadow 'arp?

<se_low>Yangus: Oh...right. Never mind, then.
See ya!
<se_high>Red: I 'ope not! I don't wanna see your ugly mug 'ere again! Got it!?
